OL,3,CHomelessness charity could close after
OL,4,Cenergy bill spirals into thousands
OL,6,FFounder Jason Parsons said: "I said
OL,7,F(to E.ON) I don't know where you're
OL,8,Fgetting your figures from, because
OL,9,Fnone of these figures tally with the
OL,10,Fbills I keep.
OL,12,F"We have to pay something because
OL,13,Fthey're going to turn us off."
OL,15,FAfter ITV West Country contacted EON,
OL,16,Fthe company wrote to Jason apologising
OL,17,Ffor his experience and offered him one
OL,18,Fhundred pounds as a goodwill gesture.
