OL,3,CHomelessness charity could close after
OL,4,Cenergy bill spirals into thousands
OL,6,FThe firm insists the bill is correct
OL,7,Fand that Jason still owes more than
OL,8,F#4,000. Jason says if the money can't
OL,9,Fbe raised, the charity would close.
OL,11,F"We are a registered charity, we don't
OL,12,Fget funding," he said. "We have to do
OL,13,Fcar boot sales, we sell things online,
OL,14,Fthat's how we raise money.
OL,16,F"Nobody gets paid anything. We issue
OL,17,Fbetween 80 and 100 meals a night and
OL,18,Fit's not just homeless, it's
OL,19,Fvulnerable people, it's people that
OL,20,Fcan afford a roof over their head but
OL,21,Fthey can't afford to feed.
