OL,6,F"We have families come down with four
OL,7,Fchildren, we give them five meals. We
OL,8,Fhelp with clothing and bedding. We'll
OL,9,Fhave to find a way to raise that money
OL,10,For we'll have to close."
OL,12,FThe charity has launched an to help
OL,13,Fpay the bills.
OL,15,FAn E.ON spokesman said: "We can
OL,16,Fconfirm that the money owed by Mr
OL,17,FParsons is correct and reflects the
OL,18,Fenergy used at the premises.
