OL,6,F"The outstanding balance which has
OL,7,Fbuilt up is the direct result of
OL,8,Funderpayments over the past few years.
OL,10,F"We have tried to contact Mr Parsons
OL,11,Fmultiple times over the past year, by
OL,12,Fphone, text and e-mail, to see if we
OL,13,Fcould set up a mutually agreeable
OL,14,Fpayment plan to help clear the debt.
OL,16,F"However, we do accept our service did
OL,17,Fnot meet our usual high standards and
OL,18,Fwe have apologised for this and
OL,19,Foffered Mr Parsons a goodwill payment
OL,20,Fto reflect this.
